![Episode40.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578167512589-WZKNOLGTZTEP1E1FWB52/Episode40.jpg)

This was fate. Ever since the first episode of Which WAS Worse concluded, it was fated for Dan The ComicMan and The Don to do battle again. This time the war has one goal. We must finally figure out which is the worst Spider-Man film of all time. (With Dan defending Spider-Man 3 and The Don advocating for Amazing Spider-Man 2) Nothing is off the table as the guys talk odd chemistry, bad haircuts, terrible vilains, and crappy dialogue in a war of words for the ages. Whether you love or hate these films, listen to us ramble incoherently in another jam packed episode of Major Issues!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

